snippet.title: BK Nostalgia 64 Trailer
snippet.description:
#BanjoKazooie #Nintendo #Nintendo64
BK Nostalgia 64 is a BK mod where you will be able to explore a Hub World inspired by N64, and visit some of the best N64 games.
Will be the definitive version of my previous mod BK Stay At Home, and will be available soon, thanks for your patience!

Become a member of my Youtube channel:
